snippet.textDisplay:
I know many of you know the meaning of the lyrics but still for those who don't understand.
Momina Mustehsan)
Baatein teri karte hue
Thak ke so jaati hoon sirhaane aasmaan
Jaane kahaan mud jaati hain
Dekhte dekhte tujhe ye galiyan

Teri tarah khushbu chale..
Taare hamari tarah raaton se mile

Endlessly reminiscing about you
I fall asleep next to the sky
I wonder where these paths disappear
As I stand here waiting for you

The fragrant breeze reminds me of you
Stars meet the sky as your heart meets mine

(Asim Azhar)
Suni naheen zamaane ne teri meri kahaaniyan
Karde koyi nawaazishen karam mehrbaniyan

The world has never heard a tale such as ours
Can someone show us some mercy and kindness?

(Momina Mustehsan)
Yeh aarzu thi ki dekhe ye duniya
Ham jaisa koi deewaana hi naheen

The wish was that the world should see
That there are no two such crazy lovers as you and me

(Asim Azhar)
Karde koyi nawaazishen karam mehrbaaniyaan

Can someone show us some mercy and kindness?

(Momina Mustehsan)
Raat andheri mein chhup rahe the
Gum ek sawera dhoond rahe the
Sadiyon se jaise jaag rahe the
Pyar ko apne dhaanp rahe the

We were hiding in the dark night
We were trying to find a lost dawn
It was as if we had been sleepless since centuries
We were concealing our love for each other

(Asim Azhar)
Phir gir pade
Koyi mila naa sahaara kya kare

Then we missed our step
There was no one to save us from stumbling

(Momina Mustehsan)
Suni nahi zamaane ne teri meri kahaaniyaan

The world has never heard a tale such as ours

Tera woh pyaar yaad aayega
Bhoolega naa ye dil mera
Kya ho gaya socha na tha

Tera woh pyar, Tera woh pyar
Tera woh pyar, Tera woh pyar (x2)

The memory of your love will stay with me
My heart will not let me forget
Never imagined that this could happen

The memory of your love
The memory of your love

(Asim Azhar)
Teri woh khamoshiyaan
Kah deti theen woh sabhi jo tu nah kah saki

Your silences would say to me
All that you could not bring yourselves to say

(Momina Mustehsan)
Kaise bataati tujhe
Sharmaati thi main jaise
Aanchal mein jalta diya

How could I tell you what was in my heart?
I felt hesitant as a lamp glimmering from behind a veil

(Asim Azhar)
Khoye kahaan mujh ko bataa...

Tell me where we disappeared

(Momina Mustehsan)
Tera woh pyaar yaad aayega
Bhoolega nah yeh dil mera

(Asim Azhar)
Tera woh pyaar yaad aayega
Bhoolega nah yeh dil mera

(Momina Mustehsan)
Kya ho gaya socha na tha.

This song is wonderful as the lyrics are.
Pakistan is a great country great talented people. I love you pakistan from an Indian.

snippet.textDisplay:
We all know that there will be always some political dispute among Pakistan and India. What the people can do is ignore all the shit and love eachother. We all have the same forefathers, like it or not. Let's tell stories of love, talent and music instead. Because at the end of the day, we are all humans, separated by barriers. LET'S REMOVE THOSE BARRIERS AND EMBRACE THE GOODNESS OF LIFE.
Love From,
Pakistan.
